node.text:
I'll never forget how you walked in my studio  session to hear the songs that later became 
"No Mercy".... First thing you said to me with a straight face was... "Don't take this asswhoopin tomorrow personally."😂 (Lakers vs Hawks ) We laughed and talked and vibed on a level only  only warriors who'd weathered excruciating storms would understand. I watched you and @killermike exchange philosophy on marijuana legalization in the US & the NBA. We bonded and learned from each other things we had no idea of in one another's lifestyles & professions. I'd heard so much about you & saw so much of you & rooted against you in prison (which we laughed about when you asked me "let me know how that goes"🤣) but gained an unwavering amount of respect for you this evening. We stayed up til 3-4am talking shit and you went to train right after that!!! A dedication I had never witnessed first hand before prior to this experience. Thank you for your example of discipline & resilience & everything else you contributed
(even STILL) to the culture. We miss you and hold you & your family's legacy up in high esteem. May you & GiGi feel the love & celebration from wherever you've evolved to. Love & Respect G @kobebryant
